{"vv40:0.1":"Vimanavatthu ","vv40:0.2":"Itthivimana ","vv40:0.3":"Manjitthakavagga ","vv40:0.4":"2. Pabhassaravimanavatthu ","vv40:1.1":"“Pabhassaravaravannanibhe, ","vv40:1.2":"Surattavatthavasane; ","vv40:1.3":"Mahiddhike candanaruciragatte, ","vv40:1.4":"Ka tvam subhe devate vandase mamam. ","vv40:2.1":"Pallanko ca te mahaggho, ","vv40:2.2":"Nanaratanacittito ruciro; ","vv40:2.3":"Yattha tvam nisinna virocasi, ","vv40:2.4":"Devarajariva nandane vane. ","vv40:3.1":"Kim tvam pure sucaritamacari bhadde, ","vv40:3.2":"Kissa kammassa vipakam; ","vv40:3.3":"Anubhosi devalokasmim, ","vv40:3.4":"Devate pucchitacikkha; ","vv40:3.5":"Kissa kammassidam phalan”ti. ","vv40:4.1":"“Pindaya te carantassa, ","vv40:4.2":"Malam phanitanca adadam bhante; ","vv40:4.3":"Tassa kammassidam vipakam, ","vv40:4.4":"Anubhomi devalokasmim. ","vv40:5.1":"Hoti ca me anutapo, ","vv40:5.2":"Aparaddham dukkhitanca me bhante; ","vv40:5.3":"Saham dhammam nassosim, ","vv40:5.4":"Sudesitam dhammarajena. ","vv40:6.1":"Tam tam vadami bhaddante, ","vv40:6.2":"‘Yassa me anukampiyo koci; ","vv40:6.3":"Dhammesu tam samadapetha’, ","vv40:6.4":"Sudesitam dhammarajena. ","vv40:7.1":"Yesam atthi saddha buddhe, ","vv40:7.2":"dhamme ca sangharatane; ","vv40:7.3":"Te mam ativirocanti, ","vv40:7.4":"ayuna yasasa siriya. ","vv40:8.1":"Patapena vannena uttaritara, ","vv40:8.2":"Anne mahiddhikatara maya deva”ti. ","vv40:9.1":"Pabhassaravimanam dutiyam. "}